page.title: 10Local Events
page.content: Eight members of the place youth{club enjoyed a trip out to Bridlington last saturday.They did alot of diffrent activities,including water skiing.Conisbrough garden{society}are to hold their half_yearly general meeting is at Ivanhoe w.m.c. tommorow, saturday at noon.A racing trip to York on 13th July by the alma into the magnet cub .All the seats have been taken.This is always a popular annual event.The Eagle and Child Public House has had to cancel its sea fishing trip to Whitby,due to rough weather.It is hoped to arrange the trip for a later date.The Lord Conyers panel games team lost by eight{games}to three when they played the Trades Club in Denaby last week.
